Extension Word: Edit Documents for Chrome

Easily customize your Word Online experience with this Chrome extension! Adjust the page opacity and change the background color on https://word.cloud.microsoft using an intuitive slider and color picker. Enhance visibility and comfort while working on documents directly in your browser.
